<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>CuteURL — Error</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background: #f0f4f8; color: #1a202c; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; padding: 2rem; }
    .box { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.08); text-align: center; max-width: 480px; }
    h1 { color: #e53e3e; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: .5rem; }
    p { color: #718096; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    a { color: #2b6cb0; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="box">
    <h1>Oops</h1>
    <p><%= message %></p>
    <a href="/">← Back to CuteURL</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
